If only you had been born 40 years earlier.

36
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,690
Left and Right Guardians,

37
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,130
are all our people assembled?

38
00:03:54,230 --> 00:03:56,350
The Sect Mistress and the Saintess have yet to arrive.

39
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:58,590
Of the Four Great Kings of our sect,

40
