That's more like it.

55
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:52,660
Let's go.

56
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:55,960
Grandma!

57
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:03,750
Greetings, Junior Sect Master.
I am Si Yunxiang, the Saintess.

58
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:05,140
Saintess?

59
00:06:05,930 --> 00:06:08,270
Our current Saintess is much more well-behaved.

60
00:06:08,730 --> 00:06:11,080
The last one was a real troublemaker.

61
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:12,630
- I'm still here! - Grandma...

62
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:14,570
What's your problem, old fool?

63
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,560
Mu,

64
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,570
Xiang is from our Si family.

65
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:21,730
After the Grandmaster met her,

66
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,450
he personally trained her for several years.

67
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:27,150
No wonder she always reminded me of Grandma Si.

68
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,630
King Qian still hasn't arrived?

69
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,330
Not yet.

70
00:06:32,930 --> 00:06:33,560
Look into it.

71
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,360
See that King Qian's family is well cared for.

72
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:39,890
Imperial Preceptor,

73
00:06:40,700 --> 00:06:41,430
there's unrest in Yongzhou.

74
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:43,090
The senior members of the Heavenly Demon Sect
have gathered there,

75
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,140
and the City Lord's Mansion vanished into thin air.

76
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,000
I see.

77
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,730
It's the top demonic sect.

78
00:06:49,030 --> 00:06:49,930
We cannot take them lightly.

79
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:53,020
If you knew who their Grandmaster is,

80
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:55,300
you wouldn't be so alarmed.

81
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,090
Their Grandmaster?

82
00:06:57,730 --> 00:07:00,030
He was the Grand Chancellor of the Imperial Academy.

83
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,690
So he has been hiding here all this time.

84
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:04,790
Could he be...?

85
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,030
You're overthinking it.

86
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,460
Years ago, I traveled the land

87
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:10,130
to learn from all the great sects,

88
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:12,890
but I found each one hoarding its knowledge

89
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:14,330
and guarding its teachings,

90
00:07:14,530 --> 00:07:16,990
which stifled the wider progress
of cultivation arts and techniques.

91
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,840
So I began visiting them,

92
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:22,250
hoping to tear down those barriers.

93
00:07:23,230 --> 00:07:24,620
The first person I met

94
00:07:25,330 --> 00:07:27,230
was the Grandmaster of the Heavenly Demon Sect.

95
00:07:28,430 --> 00:07:31,360
He was the first to cast aside sectarian pride

96
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,800
and teach me sincerely,

97
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,090
showing me a clear path forward.

98
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:39,790
He even personally recommended me to the Dao Master.

99
00:07:40,730 --> 00:07:43,290
Because of his recommendation,
the Dao Master treated me with favor

100
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:45,490
and granted me access to "The Fourteen Dao Sword Forms".

101
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,390
He also helped me gain entry to the Great Thunderclap Sect

102
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,560
to receive the teachings of Rulai.

103
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:54,890
Though he never revealed his identity,

104
00:07:55,330 --> 00:07:56,490
he couldn't hide it from me.

105
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:58,290
Nor did he try.

106
00:07:58,910 --> 00:07:59,430
(Hall of the Imperial Academy)

107
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:01,570
I invited him to oversee the Imperial Academy

108
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,530
not because of his skills,

109
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:06,290
nor because of his identity as
the Grandmaster of the Heavenly Demon Sect,

110
00:08:06,700 --> 00:08:10,190
but because of his broad-mindedness.

111
00:08:11,730 --> 00:08:16,110
He was the first person I ever met
with such purity and magnanimity of heart.

112
00:08:16,250 --> 00:08:16,800
(Hall of the Imperial Academy)

113
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:20,360
Only he was fit to lead the Imperial Academy.

114
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:22,990
He is both my teacher

115
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:25,060
and my companion on the Way.

116
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:27,060
If he is your companion,

117
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:28,990
why did he resign and leave?

118
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:34,049
Likely for the next Sect Master of the Heavenly Demon Sect.

119
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:38,690
I will go and meet this new Sect Master myself.

120
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,059
If our paths align, he will thrive.

121
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:43,659
If they diverge, he will perish.

122
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:56,150
A blessed day,

123
00:08:57,460 --> 00:08:59,320
a fortunate hour.

124
00:09:00,330 --> 00:09:02,030
As heaven and earth unite,

125
00:09:03,230 --> 00:09:05,850
endless blessings descend!

126
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:14,290
Disciples of the Heavenly Saint Sect,
welcome the Junior Sect Master to the throne!

127
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:20,560
Welcome to the throne, Junior Sect Master.

128
00:09:25,230 --> 00:09:28,160
Welcome to the throne, Junior Sect Master!

129
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:35,290
Welcome to the throne, Junior Sect Master!

130
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,600
Grandmaster,

131
00:09:36,830 --> 00:09:39,520
why do we call the Sect Master's inauguration
an enthronement?

132
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,360
Isn't "enthronement" for emperors?

133
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:44,630
In the golden age of our sect,

134
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,330
we ruled six nations.

135
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,880
