136
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:52,450
Calling the Sect Master's inauguration
an enthronement was, in truth,

137
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:54,990
an honor for the emperors.

138
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:57,090
(Hall of the Sage's Heart)
But times have changed.

139
00:09:57,700 --> 00:10:00,960
Now, a nation is the greatest of all sects.

140
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:05,120
A sect can no longer make everyone its disciple,

141
00:10:05,210 --> 00:10:06,530
but a nation

142
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,560
