151
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,760
He must be eliminated.

152
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:13,260
Understood.

153
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:17,310
The Imperial Preceptor of Yankang has adopted
the Heavenly Demon Sect's doctrine as his guiding principle.

154
00:11:17,660 --> 00:11:20,480
Yankang Nation has effectively become
a vast extension of the Heavenly Demon Sect.

155
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:22,340
What should our Dao Sect do about that?

156
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:27,360
The Imperial Preceptor's ability cannot match his ambition.

157
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:30,660
History has seen geniuses greater than him

158
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,700
and empires grander than Yankang Nation,

159
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:37,560
yet they all turned to dust
and then to the Great Wasteland in the end.

160
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:40,930
This world is far more complicated than he imagines.

161
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:45,030
When he suffers a crushing defeat, he will learn the truth.

162
00:11:46,730 --> 00:11:50,020
Although Mount Shenglin now lies beyond the heavens,

163
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:52,430
it was once part of the mortal world.

164
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:56,670
When our founding master Wei Suifeng first came here,

165
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:58,790
he saw a woodcutter

166
00:11:59,100 --> 00:12:01,380
felling this very pine.

167
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:05,990
Each time the axe struck, the tree would regrow

168
00:12:06,130 --> 00:12:07,420
the missing piece.

169
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:10,730
Realizing he had met a sage,

170
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:12,460
the founding master sought his teaching.

171
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:15,680
The woodcutter sat upon this rock and began to preach,

172
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,860
continuing for decades.

173
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:24,550
The founding master later compiled the sage's words

174
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:28,270
and wrote "The Ultimate Heavenly Demon Codex" for the world.

175
00:12:29,430 --> 00:12:30,230
Qin Mu,

176
00:12:31,230 --> 00:12:34,040
will you inherit the founding master's virtues, wisdom,

177
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:35,760
principles, and knowledge?

178
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,390
Yes, I will.

179
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:41,460
Then

180
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:42,930
the sect will be yours.

181
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,060
You must bear its weight.

182
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,630
I will.

183
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:50,290
This is the Sage Rock

184
00:12:50,660 --> 00:12:51,890
and Sage Seat.

185
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:56,490
The woodcutter sage
and the founding master shared no bloodline

186
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:57,590
or personal gain.

187
00:12:58,330 --> 00:13:01,430
He taught simply because one sought the Way.

188
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,490
The Saint Sect has endured for over 20,000 years.

189
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,730
Once you sit upon the Sage Rock,

190
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:08,190
you become the Sect Master and Saint Master,

191
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:11,660
charged with passing on our teachings, guarding our faith,

192
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:14,890
and carrying the Heavenly Saint Sect into the future.

193
00:13:20,530 --> 00:13:22,990
We pay our respects to you, Sect Master!

194
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:35,380
(Great Thunderclap Sect)

195
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:42,990
Fresh reports say

196
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:46,640
the prefect of Yongzhou
is Elder Yulin of the Heavenly Demon Sect.

197
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:50,480
Yongzhou has become a fortress of the sect.

198
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:54,660
Si Yunxiang, who defeated the Chanzi,
has also appeared there.

199
00:13:55,130 --> 00:13:57,560
She is likely one of their disciples.

200
00:13:58,300 --> 00:14:01,980
This gathering may be related to their new Sect Master.

201
00:14:01,980 --> 00:14:02,520
(Great Thunderclap Sect)

202
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:06,360
The Heavenly Demon Sect
has been without a leader for over 40 years.

203
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:07,670
It has been riven by internal strife,

204
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,480
leaving it no time to meddle in Yankang's reforms.

205
00:14:10,950 --> 00:14:11,300
(Great Thunderclap Sect)

206
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:14,660
But just a while ago, the Imperial Academy
used one of the Heavenly Demon Sect's disciples

207
00:14:14,730 --> 00:14:17,350
to defeat our Chanzi.

208
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:20,130
If this was their new Sect Master's doing,

209
00:14:20,330 --> 00:14:22,990
we cannot let it pass.

210
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,520
Understood.

211
00:14:25,060 --> 00:14:26,350
There is one more matter.

212
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:30,460
Junior Brother Ma came out from the Great Wasteland.

213
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:34,540
Fate moves as it must.

214
00:14:35,230 --> 00:14:38,050
Go investigate the new Sect Master
of the Heavenly Demon Sect.

215
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:42,660
I will personally settle this karmic debt.

216
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,190
Li Tianxing,

217
00:14:45,530 --> 00:14:46,930
the new Sect Master has ascended the throne.

218
00:14:47,430 --> 00:14:49,940
Aren't you going to appear and pass on our sect's arts?

219
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:52,390
Do you mean to take them to the grave?

220
00:15:20,230 --> 00:15:23,400
I obey the law of the sect.

221
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,810
So Grandma's inner demon was Master Li all along.

222
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,540
Traveler,

223
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:45,870
you have watched from there for a long time.

224
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,530
What have you seen?

225
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:51,890
Please enlighten me, Sage.

226
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:29,990
Traveler,

227
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:34,460
your kin are already bones in their graves.

228
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:37,790
You have stood here watching for 100 years.

229
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:39,790
Have you seen anything?

230
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:42,730
Humans, demons, ghosts, and spirits

231
00:16:42,830 --> 00:16:44,360
all follow their courses.

232
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:49,720
All creatures follow their own natural patterns.

233
00:16:50,530 --> 00:16:53,930
That is the great constant of existence.

234
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:58,620
So the Great Unity Technique
of "The Ultimate Heavenly Demon Codex"

235
00:16:58,680 --> 00:17:00,630
was hidden in the Sage's discourse.

236
00:17:02,530 --> 00:17:03,460
How much one grasps

237
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:05,560
depends on one's own fortune.

238
00:17:18,329 --> 00:17:19,260
Grandmaster,

239
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:21,890
the transmission is complete.

240
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:24,560
I must now seek a way to break free.

241
00:17:24,829 --> 00:17:26,390
Only by destroying her (him)

242
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:29,720
can I devote myself wholly to cultivation
and advance further.

243
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:32,870
It is not yet certain who will destroy whom.

244
00:17:35,830 --> 00:17:36,550
Grandmaster,

245
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,670
when Mu wakes, tell him

246
00:17:39,230 --> 00:17:40,690
to come home for the New Year.

247
00:17:45,130 --> 00:17:45,830
I'm leaving.

248
