(Whatever departs from it is heresy.
To follow one's true will and live in full accord)

251
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,300
(with nature is the Way." This is the foundation
of the Heavenly Saint Sect's creed and the opening tenet)

252
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:09,450
(of "The Ultimate Heavenly Demon Codex.")

