255
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:23,390
The founding master gained endless insight

256
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,860
yet was still not satisfied,

257
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:27,490
so he asked the woodcutter...

258
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:29,530
May I ask, Sage,

259
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,590
how can I become a sage?

